AT.name: Chimpuzzle Pro
AT.description: Chimpuzzle Pro is a puzzle game set in a unique jungle environment. You are the God of the game to help a monkey called “Beebo” out to reach his bananas. To help him out, you have to put blocks on the right places which Beebo can walk or climb on.
